Author: lshimaru
Text: I’m definitely going to try but I don’t want to spend inordinate amounts of time away from home like I do with my parents since I actually like my girlfriend so I’d probably have to eat dinner every day

Author: AngeloLacrime
Text: I worked my fasting schedule around other people's schedules so nobody sees how little I eat. I get away with 48 hour fasts that way.
